data.description: Upon entering, you'll be greeted by the charming layout of this home. The kitchen boasts a breakfast bar, a walk-in pantry, a cozy nook, and sleek stainless-steel appliances. Spanning over 1,800+ square feet, this residence features three bedrooms, two and a half bathrooms, a detached two-car garage, and a versatile flex room. The master suite offers a generous walk-in closet with double hanging shelves, an optional raised coffered ceiling, and a double sink vanity in the master bathroom.    This community also offers various entertainment areas, parks, and a fitness center. It is conveniently located just 10 miles from Orlando International Airport and less than 20 miles from downtown Orlando, which boasts incredible shopping, vibrant nightlife, diverse dining options, entertainment venues, world-class golf courses, museums, professional sports teams, and much more. Additionally, the theme parks are only a 25-minute drive from this home, making it an ideal location for enjoying all that the area has to offer. " THE SELLER IS MOTIVATED TO PROVIDE $ 10,000.00 TOWARDS CLOSING COSTS"
